moxie

Annotation Type GroupOptions


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface GroupOptions
    Denotes that Moxie.autoMock() should use the specified options when creating the Group that will be injected into this field.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      MoxieOptions[] value
      Specifies MoxieOptions to be used when creating a group to be injected into this field.
